{"tid":1858727,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要說「解散警隊，刻不容緩」。嘗試說「解散速龍，刻不容緩。」","createTime":"2020-02-03T01:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T07:58:08.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4a86046d97e2e28802b772378a490b24c02641d7","tid":1858727,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V7sYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=d9b08178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n速龍小隊，於2014年6月成立，係一隊專捉示威者的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n在2014年以前，香港一直都係和平示威之都，一直警民關係良好，舉世聞名。<br />\n<br />\n自速龍小隊成立後，警民衝突不斷，警暴升級，示威者也反抗，導致流血衝突不斷。<br />\n<br />\n有人質疑：解散警隊，香港難以維持社會秩序。重組警隊，實行上亦好困難<br />\n<br />\n但解散速龍，絕對對社會治安無影響，對香港人百利而無一害。"},{"pid":"c02e89992423cc08491e0a58a3184bdd26e3bb45","tid":1858727,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"速龍小隊成立前，警方非常克制。<br />\n速龍小隊成立後，警方失去常態。<br />\n<br />\n解散速龍，刻不容緩。"},{"pid":"f16063ea07b5bd07529d44cdace219567a86750d","tid":1858727,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:31:10.000Z","msg":"解散不如遞介出境"},{"pid":"285513b028cb18b5d583f9e8b3e45941ea4f47aa","tid":1858727,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a86046d97e2e28802b772378a490b24c02641d7","tid":1858727,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%2588%